{"id":14967,"date":"2021-05-10T14:01:43","date_gmt":"2021-05-10T08:31:43","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/?page_id=14967"},"modified":"2023-04-24T16:02:22","modified_gmt":"2023-04-24T10:32:22","slug":"thailand","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/destination-wedding\/thailand\/","title":{"rendered":"Thailand Destination Wedding"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height=&#8221;50px&#8221; el_class=&#8221;height30&#8243;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;flexrow&#8221;][vc_column width=&#8221;1\/4&#8243; el_class=&#8221;flextwo gt-custom-sidebar-column&#8221;][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id=&#8221;destination-package-indian-sidebar&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column width=&#8221;3\/4&#8243; el_class=&#8221;second-div-text flexone&#8221;][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Tips For a Destination Wedding in Thailand&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">In order to have a grand destination wedding in Thailand, you need to be properly prepared. While we at ATW Travels take care of everything, there are certain things you should remember as well. Creating a checklist always helps to ensure everything gets done smoothly, such as checking out the venue beforehand, meeting the vendors, and finalizing everything as soon as you start planning the wedding, securing all the travel documents, and checking the local travel requirements.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Cost of Thailand Destination Wedding Package&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A Thailand destination wedding cost from ATW Travels depends on the package you choose. We can customize your wedding package based on your budget and preferences.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Part of Thailand for A Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Couples can choose from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.atwtravels.com\/packages\/international\/asia\/thailand-tour-packages\/\">best destination wedding venues in Thailand<\/a> from ATW Travels\u2019 catalogue. Some of the most alluring parts of Thailand to host a destination wedding are Bangkok, Pattaya, Phuket, Koh Samui, Chiang Mai, Krabi, Kanchanaburi, Sukhothai, Hua Hin, and Pai.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Thailand Beach for Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A beach destination wedding in Thailand is indeed a dream come true for many couples because Thailand is filled with gorgeous beaches. Some of those beaches include Railay Beach, Nai Harn Beach, Haad Rin, Phra Nang Cave Beach, Maya Bay, Pattaya Beach, Chaweng Noi Beach, Freedom Beach, Bottle Beach, Ao Prao Beach, Sairee Beach, and Hua Hin Beach.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Best Thailand Resorts to Stay in For Destination Wedding&#8221; font_container=&#8221;tag:h3|text_align:left&#8221;][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The best destination wedding resorts in Thailand are made available to you from ATW Travels. Thailand has numerous stunning resorts for you to host your destination weddings, such as Six Senses Yao Noi, Centara Grand Beach Resort, Avista Hideaway, Movenpick Resort &amp; Spa, The Chill Resort and Spa, The Surin, Pimalai Resort and Spa, Phi Phi Island Village Beach Resort, Sea Sand Sun Resort and Villas, Centara Grand Beach Resort &amp; Villas, Bo Phut Resort &amp; Spa, Soneva Kiri, JW Marriott Khao Lak Resort &amp; Spa, Sandalwood Luxury Villas, and Devasom Hua Hin Resort.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Follow our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/atwtravels.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Instagram profile<\/a> to know about the latest offers and discounts.<\/p>\n<p>[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner]<div class=\"st-faq-new st-faq\">\r\n    <h4>FAQs About Our Thailand Destination Wedding Packages<\/h4>\r\n                                <div class=\"item active\">\r\n                    <div class=\"header\">\r\n                        <i class=\"input-icon field-icon fa\"><svg height=\"18px\" width=\"18px\" version=\"1.1\" id=\"Layer_1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/1999\/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\"\r\n     viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" style=\"enable-background:new 0 0 24 24;\" xml:space=\"preserve\">\r\n\r\n<g fill=\"#5E6D77\">\r\n    <path d=\"M5.25,24c-0.116,0-0.232-0.027-0.336-0.079C4.659,23.793,4.5,23.536,4.5,23.25V19.5H2.25C1.009,19.5,0,18.491,0,17.25v-15\r\n        C0,1.009,1.009,0,2.25,0h19.5C22.991,0,24,1.009,24,2.25v15c0,1.241-1.009,2.25-2.25,2.25H11.5l-5.8,4.35\r\n        C5.571,23.947,5.411,24,5.25,24z M2.25,1.5C1.836,1.5,1.5,1.836,1.5,2.25v15C1.5,17.664,1.836,18,2.25,18h3\r\n        C5.664,18,6,18.336,6,18.75v3l4.8-3.6c0.129-0.097,0.289-0.15,0.45-0.15h10.5c0.414,0,0.75-0.336,0.75-0.75v-15\r\n        c0-0.414-0.336-0.75-0.75-0.75H2.25z\"\/>\r\n    <path d=\"M12,12c-0.414,0-0.75-0.336-0.75-0.75v-0.256c-0.001-0.952,0.602-1.805,1.5-2.122c0.897-0.317,1.5-1.17,1.5-2.121\r\n        c0-0.6-0.234-1.165-0.66-1.59c-0.425-0.426-0.99-0.66-1.59-0.66c-0.601,0-1.166,0.234-1.591,0.659\r\n        C9.984,5.584,9.75,6.149,9.75,6.75C9.75,7.164,9.414,7.5,9,7.5S8.25,7.163,8.25,6.75c0-2.067,1.683-3.749,3.75-3.749\r\n     